<!-- Hero -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>CRS Draw Predictions 2026 — Express Entry Cutoff Score Forecast</h1>
    <p>Projected CRS cutoff scores for all Express Entry draw types in 2026 — based on IRCC historical draw data, immigration level targets, pool size trends, and category-based selection patterns.</p>
    <div class="pill-row">
      <span class="pill">Updated April 2026</span>
      <span class="pill">All Draw Types Covered</span>
      <span class="pill">Historical Data Analysis</span>
